<glsa id="201206-24">
  <title>Apache Tomcat: Multiple vulnerabilities</title>
  <synopsis>Multiple vulnerabilities were found in Apache Tomcat, the worst of
    which allowing to read, modify and overwrite arbitrary files.
  </synopsis>
